<!--
    Norwegian Bokmål — nb
    Script : Latin; LTR.
    Approx.: ~5 M speakers (Norway).
    Register: Standard Bokmål (riksmål-influenced written standard).
    Notes  : Android tag "nb" covers Bokmål, which is used by ~85–90 % of
             Norwegian writers.  Nynorsk ("nn") has a separate tag but is not
             added here due to its small share.  "Binge drinking" → episodisk
             stordrinking / fyllefest — the formal term episodisk stordrinking
             is used in health-care contexts and is preferred here.
    Source : Translated from values-de/strings.xml (German source of truth).
-->
